LUTAR-1#1 Warning
LUT drives async reset alert  
LUT cell u_soc/u_rst_sync/sys_sync[0]_i_1, with 2 or more inputs, drives asynchronous preset/clear pin(s) u_soc/u_rst_sync/sys_sync_reg[0]/CLR, u_soc/u_rst_sync/sys_sync_reg[1]/CLR. The LUT may glitch and trigger an unexpected reset, even if it is a properly timed path.
